data.title: francesco maria emanuele gaetani villabianca
data.meta_description: Descrizione della Sicilia e storie siciliane di Villabianca (Francesco Maria Emanuele Gaetani marchese di Villabianca) - a cura di Salvo Di Matteo e una grande selezione di libri, arte e articoli da collezione disponibile su AbeBooks.it.

Bound in genuine leather with Satin ribbon page markers and Spine with raised gilt bands. A perfect gift for your loved ones. NO changes have been made to the original text. This is NOT a retyped or an ocr'd reprint. Illustrations, Index, if any, are included in black and white. Each page is checked manually before printing. Sewing binding for longer life, where the book block is actually sewn (smythe sewn/section sewn) with thread before binding which results in a more durable type of binding. Pages: 471.
